==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grozing iron
<hw>Gro"zing i"ron</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A tool with a
hardened steel point, formerly used instead of a diamond for cutting
glass.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Plumbing)</fld> <def>A tool for smoothing the
solder joints of lead pipe.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grub</ent>⟦br⟧
